xIMUcppAPI is a bridge between original C# 'xIMU API 13.1' and native C/C++ , visual C++ MFC.
You can use 'xIMUcppAPI' in any C or C++ or Visual C++ MFC projects.
Basically 'xIMUcppAPI' is a C++/CLI wrapper around original 'xIMU API' written in C#.

The following may help you how to use it.

http://harinadha.wordpress.com/

Original C# xIMU API is here http://www.x-io.co.uk/node/9
